    public class ProjectInProjectActivity
extends ProjectActivity
    This Activity is created when a new project is to be displayed from a ProjectActivity.

    This is exactly the same as the ProjectActivity, but having a different Activity object type allows avoiding to break the navigation history (Activity stack).

    FIXME perhaps there is a smarter way to do that.
